title: Woodmancote murders: Family of four and their dog found dead at home in West Sussex village
description: Police not looking for anyone else in connection with 'isolated incident'
content:
A murder investigation has been launched after a family of four were found dead at a home in West Sussex.
The bodies of two adults and two children were found at an address on Duffield Lane in the village of Woodmancote on Sunday evening. Their dog was also … [+19484 chars]
